data.description: You don't want to miss the opportunity to purchase this hard to find one-level ranch style home in the Cascade Heights area of Atlanta. This 3BR/1.5BA home features original hardwood floors throughout the home, separate formal living & dining room, large den that has been converted to an additional bedroom. The home is perched on a hill overlooking the street on wide lot that extends 235 ft. +/- deep. It is within walking distance to West Manor Park, close to schools, shopping, golf courses, restaurants, shopping, expressway, and airport. This is an Estate Sale.  Property is being sold "as is".
